name: Amelia Wood
profile_summary: Our user is a 28-year-old straight woman of White Caucasian ethnicity, who goes by the pronouns of She/Her/Hers. She has an accomplished academic background, having graduated from the University of California, Los Angeles. Bilingual in English and Spanish, she is a woman of virtue, valuing Honesty, Compassion, and Independence. Her interests lie in Reading, Hiking, and Playing the guitar. Though she identifies as Agnostic, she leans Liberal in her political views. Her intention in dating is to find a life partner within a Monogamous relationship. She does not have any children at the moment, but she does want them in the future. She's a cat lover and marks her zodiac as an Aries. According to the MBTI Personality type, she is an INTJ. She enjoys an active lifestyle, indulges in drinking socially but abstains from smoking, marijuana, and drugs.
